<p>Welcome to our lovely holiday apartments, located in the original heart of a charming seaside town. Our apartments offer the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and relaxation for your next getaway.</p>
<p>One of the highlights of our location is its proximity to the beach. Just a fifteen minute walk away, you'll find yourself on a picturesque sandy beach surrounded by refreshing waters. Whether you want to sunbathe, swim, or simply relax and enjoy the view, the beach is the perfect place to do so.</p>
<p>Our apartments are also located near the old church. This historic landmark is a must-see for anyone interested in the rich history and cultural heritage of the area.</p>
<p>For those in need of essential items, you'll be pleased to know that there is a pharmacy just a few steps away. Whether you need medication or toiletries, you won't have to go far to find what you need. And just a few steps further you'll find a variety of stores, boutiques, and restaurants.</p>